snippet.title: The Sims 3 Into the Future - Gameplay - Building a Dystopia
snippet.description:
Your Sims actions in the present will affect their future with The Sims 3 Into the Future!  Will your build a dystopia? Watch this gameplay demonstration.

This expansion pack is now available. You can pick it up at your local retailer or on Origin: 
http://bit.ly/FutureSims3
